Summary: Two UFO'S spotted at gas station
divs: Sighting DetailsPulled into gas station, looked up and saw two ufo's flying toward Lake Huron. Made no sound, and were brighter than nearby Venus. Ufo's powered up and faded out. Both were traveling the same direction and altitude. Witnessed by my girlfriend and her brother, and two people at the gas station. One was the clerk who came out of the store. Stepped out of truck and got my digital camera. Took a few pics with the flash on, then turned on the video mode. Got two clips.
